a.xlink:title: A widget for sorting and filtering card sets in the Printing Selector.
Updates the display by clearing the layout and loading new sets for the current card.
Updates the sorting order (ascending or descending).
Updates the sorting setting in the application settings.
Clears all widgets from the flow layout.

Adds a widget to the flow layout within the FlowWidget.
Filters a list of card sets based on the search text.

Prepend card printings that are contained in the deck to the list of printings.
